#

Crispy Chicken Burger

25 min
$8.5
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

EggGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinContains Gluten

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

QuickComfort FoodAmerican

Description

Enjoy a crunchy, savory chicken burger that's quick to prepare and utterly satisfying!

Ingredients

  • chicken breast (boneless): 2 pieces
  • bread crumbs: 1 cup
  • flour: 1/2 cup
  • egg: 1 large
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1/2 teaspoon
  • burger buns: 2 pieces
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
